messages.text:
Nit: Move this above the post_params fields (and in the other .json file too)

We could also try and distribute these fields amongst the other fields above, but that would imply we should reorder things over in TemplateURL too, which would be kind of a mess, I think.  But maybe that'd be better.

messages.author: Peter Kasting
messages.text:
TBH I probably wouldn't add this test.

It's so low-level it's nearly equivalent to just calling a simple setter and getter and verifying they return the same thing.  Not worth it IMO.

Testing that this field properly affects the actual Search/NTP machinery _is_ appropriate and hopefully is covered by search_unittest.cc.
